Flask_socketio

What does this technology (library/framework/service) accomplish for you?
Flask-SocketIO gives Flask applications access to low latency bi-directional communications between the clients and the server.

How does this technology accomplish what it does?
Installation:  $ pip install flask-socketio

@socketio.on("message")
When using SocketIO, messages are received by both parties as events. 
Our code use @socketio.on("message") to create a server-side event handler for “string” event. This can help us to create chat function. 

Code used: https://flask-socketio.readthedocs.io/en/latest/

